Anſw. No: They are written to thee, even to thee; that is, to every one, that they might have their Truſt only in God; that is, find the Rock of Divine Veracity, and Infallibility, and have no need to truſt in Men; 
   •
ut to know the certainty of the Words of Truth, and be able to anſwer the Words of Truth, either to thoſe that adviſe with them, as Friends, or challenge them, as Enemies.
